data.description: Do you want a spacious home? Look no further! This two-story home has so much to offer! The first floor features the living room with surround sound, an eat-in kitchen with a spacious island, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and the master bedroom/master bath is located downstairs as well as a half bath for your guests. The second floor has the three additional bedrooms with a full bath and a spacious bonus area to be used as a den, office or hobby room. You choose!  Laundry room is located on second floor and all bedrooms have walk-in closets! Entertaining guests? Relax under the covered patio and enjoy the spacious backyard. This home shows pride in ownership! Call for a showing today!
